ing agents.  If the combination is used, blood pressure and heart rate should be monitored.', 'Antagonism', 'Due to their pressor effect, sympathomimetic amines should be used cautiously in patients with hypertension.', NULL, NULL, 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic');
